divs: Sighting DetailsI was at my girlfriends house then i looked up to the sky i saw about 6 lights 3 were at an obtuse angle and the other 3 were in a normal triangular formation the lights began fading in and out i felt as if i were in a trance or in a state of disbelief i felt angry afterwards because i had no other witnesses besides me and my camera i want that confirmation that im not crazy.
